caption:
This year’s BTA Gaming Award winner, Danielle Udogaranya of @ebonixsims, has been a leading advocate for authentic representation, driving meaningful change through innovation, education, and mentorship

The award honours individuals who are shaping a more inclusive gaming industry. Her dedication to expanding opportunities for Black creatives and pioneering new approaches continues to redefine diversity in gaming.
